featured_reviews.review_id: Worst experience ever! Unprofessional people..they make horrible mistakes in wedding cards. Totally not sincere for there work. They will definitely spoil your wedding by making poorly printed cards! And yes! If you are getting your wedding cards made from this place then do make sure that you place an order for extra cards as if you will ask for 100 cards,they will give you 90-95 cards as they say there is wastage in it. I have bought wedding cards earlier but no one gave me 95 cards instead of 100. Wastage is separate from the number of cards ordered! Pathetic service!

I bought 200 cards from this shop and 1 card price is Rs45, but they will give you 190 cards in packing. When I said to shopkeeper please eaither refund my amount of 10 card (10 x Rs45 = Rs900) or provide me 10 card, but neither he return remaining amount nor he give me 10 cards , I have bought wedding cards earlier but no one gave me 190 cards instead of 200. Wastage is separate from the number of cards ordered! Pathetic service!
Please don't buy any cards of this shops
